nodes.text: Star Wars: Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith: The Rule of Five

Star Wars: Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith: The Rule of Five is the third story arc of Marvel Comics' series Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith. Written by Charles Soule with art by Giuseppe Camuncoli, the arc comprises two issues, and was in publication from February 14 to 28, 2018.
